      Entry: 1
      Data: 'RENDER DISTANCE CULL: when on, a chunk only meshes if its column is
        within the active render distance (renderDistanceChunksPC/Mobile, radial,
        full Y column) of the player; farther chunks defer until the player approaches.
        Player edits and rebuilds bypass it.'
