      Data: 440|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: "(b) GPU mesh-from-atlas (default OFF): let GPU-resident chunks (no CPU
        mirror) build their render mesh straight from the atlas via the GPU face
        extractor with cross-slot neighbor reads \u2014 no _GpuSyncChunkBlocks, no
        CPU border pack. Requires the chunk's blocks + its neighbors to be present
        in the atlas. With ambientOcclusion off this is geometry-only; GPU AO is
        the accuracy follow-up."
