      Entry: 1
      Data: 'PERF TEST (default 1 = original behavior): iterations between Time.realtimeSinceStartup
        budget checks in the GPU mesh-decode loop. Higher = fewer Time externs in
        the hot loop, slightly coarser per-frame budgeting. Try 8.'
