      Data: 932|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: 'DEBUG/validation for the GPU-resident migration: after the normal CPU
        atlas upload, ALSO GPU->GPU repack the chunk''s column slice straight into
        its atlas slot (overwriting). If the repack mapping is correct the world
        renders identically; if wrong it renders corrupt. 0 cost when off. Leave
        OFF.'
